  "page": "Feature quote/202",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“There is entirely too much tut-tutting in <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">this realm</a>, if you ask me. All these kings would do a deal better if they put down their swords and listened to their mothers.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Tyrell\" title=\"Olenna Tyrell\">Olenna Tyrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, Sansa I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260406183807\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 98/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 292/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 17/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 519/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.439      1 -total\n100.00%    4.439      1 Template:Ref\n 63.55%    2.821      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26359-0!canonical and timestamp 20260406183807 and revision id 240713\n -->\n",
